reviews.review_text:
Time machine If you want to be transported back to this show play back this wonderful recording with headphones on. This is not only one of the better pulls from this concert, due to the technique used it actually with give you a 3d recreation of the event with 🎧. 

Outside of this it also provides a stunning two channel in room recreation of the event, with fantastic recreation of the soundstage. Couple all this together with Kyle and the crew being in a great location and you have a reference recording. 

My only wish is that Kyle and the crew would have used these mics for all of their early 80's pulls! Damn, now I want a time machine to go back there a convince them that this is the way to do it.
